com.appboy.configuration

Class AppboyConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.appboy.configuration.AppboyConfig

  • public class AppboyConfig
extends java.lang.Object
    Configuration for the Appboy SDK. This configuration has full parity with use of xml configuration. Any key found in the Appboy xml configuration is configurable here. For all parameters of the built AppboyConfig object, any field will be set to null if not set in the builder.
